title: Charming Craftsman Home Beautiful Surroundings 998
text:
Charming Craftsman Home Beautiful Surroundings 998 ad date: 10/17/2015 
Surroundings 998 Krista Lane Brookings Pristine Craftsman style custom home with open concept living space, Hardwood Floors and tile. Spacious rooms, lots of light and naturally beautiful surroundings. Put this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 3-car garage on your must see list. Deck, with a fenced secluded back yard. Over-sized large corner lot. Mature plum, lemon and apple trees. Two additional bonus rooms, all master living quarters on main, Handicap accessible. No. 15312729 $397,000 Jude Hodge, Broker
